{
  "stem": "5758.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A lot of people just died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were just wandering around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We heard, again, artillery coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of people died on the ground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The SS disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were no SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were-- we were guarded by Hungarian and Croatian soldiers with guns, anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And people just-- the hunger that we experienced is just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When you go and dig up for roots, you know what it-- what it can do to you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Finally, on the 15th of April, two days before my birthday, the British troop entered.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were sitting-- I remember, we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I couldn't walk very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sitting on the ground, and we saw these troops coming in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You would imagine that everybody would be shouting, hurray, we're free!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was absolutely quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe because we couldn't believe that this is the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Maybe because we didn't have the strength to shout.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe we-- because we only can think of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We couldn't think of anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Food, food, food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "All during the two years, hunger, that was our thought.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You got to eat to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember there was a Jewish chaplain of the British army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I later knew it was Reverend Hardman from Hendon synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We met and talked about it quite often.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were given our first hot food, but it was a big mistake.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "What they did, they gave us milk and rice with sugar, sweet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The people were grabbing at it and eating as much as they could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "A lot of them died because their stomach just couldn't-- their body couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One doctor warned us, eat it slowly, and don't eat much.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
